%N A282297 Binary representation of the x-axis, from the origin to the right edge, of the n-th stage of growth of the two-dimensional cellular automaton defined by "Rule 451", based on the 5-celled von Neumann neighborhood.
%C A282297 Initialized with a single black (ON) cell at stage zero.
%D A282297 S. Wolfram, A New Kind of Science, Wolfram Media, 2002; p. 170.
%H A282297 Robert Price, <a href="/A282297/b282297.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..126</a>
